{"tid":724893,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實以家班00後係咪唔識得人情世故","createTime":"2018-07-01T09:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T14:12:12.000Z","uid":1734,"like":9,"dislike":406,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb1a4e3e6537a113e8a7ad59365234bfb93d133","tid":724893,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"今日有個00後入黎做長散 咁有新同事加入 我地都好主動話晏就一齊出去食飯啦（平時個個帶飯 今日屈個00後請） 佢都話好 咁諗住佢識做啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到lunch 個時 我地去飲茶 叫撚到成台野食 又鮑魚雞粒炒飯 又燒賣又蝦餃 仲有幾個同事專登叫多拎返屋企做晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買單個時 我地都好識做張張單放係個新人面前 諗住佢直接出去埋單 點撚知佢拎部手機出黎計總數再除返開10 個人  佢仲好撚醒咁講每人180 啦 有多幾十我貼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我同班同事呆撚左望住佢  我忍唔住開口話 不嬲有新人都係新人請  佢老母夠膽話要留錢去畢業旅行唔肯請  之後拎左200 出黎就算 我地嬲到爆 打算之後排斥呢個00後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以家班00後真係唔識人情世故 新入職請食飯咁少事都唔得 佢地唔會係社會立足到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298a6ab31cc18c804739c56f4be15660fd24ac98","tid":724893,"uid":178800,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"負皮係比你個七頭"},{"pid":"deac269f833f23bfb7748b1bf482fc3b6e9460ba","tid":724893,"uid":170867,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"又係你牙lily-.-"},{"pid":"e7393f548ada8128401f67902af0eaea6a1fa1bb","tid":724893,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"298a6ab31cc18c804739c56f4be15660fd24ac98","tid":724893,"uid":178800,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"c